I guess you are thinking more big scale tracking/solution (?).
Indeed it is needed, but my indicated one is not for it.
It is just for "we want to use soc_pcm_close() as soc_pcm_open() error hand=
ling".

> > 	int soc_pcm_open(...)
> > 	{
> > 		static u8 id;
> >=20
> > 		/* update ID */
